&gt;     puppet_collaboration    unknown lei       
&gt;     puppet_commercial_lines unknown npds      
&gt;     puppet_nvp              windows ucce_gold 
&gt;     puppet_oracle           linux   oracle_oid
&gt;     puppet_splunk           unknown add_on

